law.text:
The Committee consists of the following 7 members:
1 individual appointed by the Governor;
as ex officio members:
the Comptroller;
the Treasurer;
the Secretary of Budget and Management; and
the Secretary of Transportation; and
as nonvoting members:
the chair of the Capital Budget Subcommittee of the Senate Budget and Taxation Committee; and
the chair of the Capital Budget Subcommittee of the House Appropriations Committee.
